{"tid":253640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發］岩岩食飯吞左條魚骨 卡左喉嚨到","createTime":"2017-05-22T14:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T09:48:37.000Z","uid":105480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b0daff3b47f5be26f9305c72263c343d03ac9f","tid":253640,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"已經嘔左兩次 但條魚骨好調皮咁仲卡左係喉嚨<br />\n 上網睇話唔好飲醋同呑飯 請問除左睇醫生仲有無其他解救方法 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚辛苦啊屌你個喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d313ae34109e43f7586bb25153c3dd92c1279590","tid":253640,"uid":45450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬仲有冇野要交帶低"},{"pid":"610979576deace2a530639baff095b946812a1f1","tid":253640,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓豬仲有冇野要交帶低</blockquote><br />\n家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117c2bb72b49281b90df8d2220bcbc07a5b8cca2","tid":253640,"uid":140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"用手了啦，仲要教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f19b5598b425126a083a25e8fc30392e79bbf80","tid":253640,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用手了啦，仲要教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n插得好入 已經唔係手可以解決得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d5456d9467bff168a93021196e3fc5ead05a12","tid":253640,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"呑一大舊飯 搞掂<br />\n(上次因為咁喺屯門醫院排左五粒鐘最後姑娘俾在舊飯我就好番)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af10448be4602