可以格硬推條骨落食道嘅<br />\n如果大條就唔好咁做啦，有機會整到流血，之前有新聞係話因為咁而失血過多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵醫生幫手好過"},{"pid":"e049bfe8873055460d80ea867f0b7fcb0c091347","tid":253640,"uid":76152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"以前細個試過，比阿媽帶左去急症室，勁多個護士同我阿媽一齊禁住我個頭加埋我對手同腳，個醫生伸個野入我喉嚨度夾返條魚骨出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我過左咁多年都仲記得個下的感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cb78676ecd4d8334dee29738368e7efaf7c626","tid":253640,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照 soft tissue neck 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"8fb9e6ad1a2d7ee4f578172714db22cf6e1d9541","tid":253640,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前細個試過，比阿媽帶左去急症室，勁多個護士同我阿媽一齊禁住我個頭加埋我對手同腳，個醫生伸個野入我喉嚨度夾返條魚骨出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我過左咁多年都仲記得個下的感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nx2 試過幾次白車去<br />\n個鉗好撚大個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591018ea744de4cb9cc6002379a293321f7025ea","tid":253640,"uid":51397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"電視廣告個呀婆教擺個碗上頭然後用筷子係咁插(好似係)"},{"pid":"8fd4dbbedc0011eef8e997a32835352808bf9baa","tid":253640,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電視廣告個呀婆教擺個碗上頭然後用筷子係咁插(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n呢個好似幾work"},{"pid":"3c31977a3d7e96f81f83642dbe126555a3e4ab97","tid":253640,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:14:31.000Z","msg":"扣喉 早兩個月先奶過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71b9025a8408c5ebeefbbe5e7b4c865353f6948","tid":253640,"uid":31296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:22:05.000Z","msg":"試過睇急症，好快搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b451b2891db3fbf7caa5ecf6f1ff57aa8a0f80e2","tid":253640,"uid":100651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T18:35:56.000Z","msg":"細個老母教話食麥芽糖等佢痴住舊骨一齊落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e31b0539d93d089af527e8d361b4d9096a083d","tid":253640,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T16:37:37.000Z","msg":"巴打最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c51a29a7e948eccea2b59e238dbfff87c3a8f0","tid":253640,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n攞條魚骨出來仲慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一站去睇急診，醫生話睇唔到我條魚骨因為我條魚骨插得太深，之後幫我轉左去耳鼻喉科。<br />\n<br />\n第二站見耳鼻喉醫生，了解左我狀況之後，叫我張大嘴巴扯實條舌頭，佢再用左個鉗幫我夾番出來，但夾左幾次都夾唔到，而我條舌頭扯得太耐就損撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後過左一粒鐘佢叫我過隔離房，用窺探鏡插入我鼻哥再直經過口腔再經過喉嚨拎番條魚骨。<br />\n<br />\n插入鼻既一剎那我成個人灰左，因為真係好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後拎左條魚骨番屋企bin屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid