"tid":253640,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我小小試過 真心辛苦 食d野都痛痛地 飲水都係</blockquote><br />\n我又咳又嘔 條魚骨都攬實我個喉嚨唔肯出來，當左我喉嚨係佢新居咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66ed8568abb66d3f2b13457e4cf43f51f582368","tid":253640,"uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"試過飲醋真係得，不過你會嘔到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e662e2959ab106c3dfb0b4808d801b08a9c1ce","tid":253640,"uid":66213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去睇醫生啦，夾硬吞野落去可能會整到食道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係急症室姑娘叫我呑飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓 急救第一個就叫人唔好亂黎<br />\n去睇醫生夾出黎再少傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吞飯會唔會整斷左一邊之後另一邊仲插住係到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25047cbbf907fca043d0e012e018f0a30465e77d","tid":253640,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呑一大舊飯 搞掂<br />\n(上次因為咁喺屯門醫院排左五粒鐘最後姑娘俾在舊飯我就好番)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真?</blockquote><br />\n鳩吹啦<br />\n上次哽親野去到分流係當緊急case<br />\n即刻搵人黎帶我入去見醫生<br />\n點會等成五粒鐘呀"},{"pid":"bf1ca32858936043126aa2dc7e1a39e9f661caf0","tid":253640,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"條骨好大條架？？？"},{"pid":"164322bb8981de9bbe278f3feb6bf9cf207deb38","tid":253640,"uid":29317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:29:3