所以卡魚骨未試過，但成日插撚到牙肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n插牙肉我反而少"},{"pid":"7c899f81328a9f459a8c5151e6c391eb2079406b","tid":253640,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我小小試過 真心辛苦 食d野都痛痛地 飲水都係</blockquote><br />\n我又咳又嘔 條魚骨都攬實我個喉嚨唔肯出來，當左我喉嚨係佢新居咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去睇醫生 佢照一照我個口 跟住就攞條雪條棍壓住條利再睇 <br />\n見到條魚骨插住左係喉嚨d肉到 <br />\n跟住攞個夾放勁入一野就攞番出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你條魚骨應該唔係插得好深，醫生要用反鏡先睇到我條魚骨，插得好鬼深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5174e8f12952357e568497e3fba92d562cb7ed68","tid":253640,"uid":117302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電視廣告個呀婆教擺個碗上頭然後用筷子係咁插(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n呢個好似幾work</blockquote><br />\n記住一路插一路講「骨落骨落」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係試過，成功骨落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815c263ce60f0c1acda6031c8c12835fd8da8922","tid":253640,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:41:32.000Z","msg":"樓豬咁快就比人開發咗第四穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ed0e9e9d53f0559c282a25cdb5d535e4bd66da","tid":253640,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T18:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電視廣告個呀婆教擺個碗上頭然後用筷子係咁插(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n呢個好似幾work</blockquote><br />\n記住一路插一路講「骨落骨落」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></block